# Privacy Policy

StoryPulse is designed to respect your privacy by default.

- The application **never connects to the internet** after installation.
- No telemetry, analytics, crash reports, or background services are included.
- All text inputs and generated videos are stored **only on your local machine** in:
  - Windows: `%USERPROFILE%\Documents\StoryPulse`
  - macOS: `~/Documents/StoryPulse`
  - Linux: `~/Documents/StoryPulse`

You can delete all data at any time via the app settings or by removing the folder.

Your stories belong to you â€” and only you.
